history.text: Do you generally like watching comedies?
Yes, I love comedies! Especially romantic comedies, but really any comedy is a great movie.
That's awesome! Yeah I agree. So what did you think of Bruce Almighty?

Bruce Almighty is hilarious! Jim Carrey
 plays his role so well.

Yes! It is definitely one of my favorite movies. Jim Carrey is hilarious in the slapstick scenes. Also I think Morgan Freeman was a good addition to the movie and I'm a sucker for anything with Jennifer Anniston in it. I'm pretty suprised about the Rotten Tomatoes score though its pretty low for how good I think the movie was.
Really? That is surprising! My whole family and all of my friends love the movie! I can't imagine that it received a low rating.

Yeah! I loved it too and I think that if you have the chance you should re-watch it
 because it is such a classic movie.
Yes! I have some free time this afternoon. I wonder if it is on Netflix. I'd love to watch it again, but don't have a DVD copy of the movie.

uid2response.feedback: The conversation was smoothed and seemed like a real conversation. My partner left the room after 5 responses. I waited 5 minutes.
